portfoliosYaml.title: portrait
portfoliosYaml.description: An astrologist once told me she sees me getting in to portrait photography, capturing the soul of a person.  Portrait photograpphy ranges from capturing the spirit or essence of a person to a professional headshot for conveying a message of confidence or openess.  It can be fashion inspired or it can be capture a person at their natural state of being.
